  - id: ITEM-011
    title: "Implement LNC format validator"
    objective: llm_format_contract_capability
    priority: p0
    status: done
    created_at_utc: 2026-03-11T09:52:00Z
    completed_at_utc: 2026-03-11T10:12:00Z
    bucket: contracts
    description: |
      Enhanced Python-based LNC format validator that checks:
      - Required header fields (@lnc version)
      - YAML syntax validity (including TAB detection)
      - Required field presence per kind (task, decision, note, code_unit)
      - ID uniqueness across LNC files
      - Task-specific validation: status, priority values
      - Decision-specific validation: options count, selected validity
    acceptance_criteria:
      - Validator runs on runtime/examples/ directory
      - Reports missing required fields with specific paths
      - Reports syntax errors with line numbers
      - Validates task status values (open, in_progress, done, cancelled)
      - Validates priority values (p0, p1, p2, p3)
      - Returns exit code 0 on valid, 1 on invalid
    stage: done
    commit_ref: null
  - id: ITEM-013
    title: "Implement runtime replay conformance harness"
    objective: runtime_replay_capability
    priority: p0
    status: done
    created_at_utc: 2026-03-11T12:12:00Z
    completed_at_utc: 2026-03-11T12:52:00Z
    bucket: runtime
    description: |
      Create a replay conformance harness that validates deterministic replay:
      - TraceCapture class for recording execution traces
      - ExecutionTrace dataclass with full state serialization
      - ReplayValidator for comparing original vs replayed traces
      - ConformanceHarness for running multiple iterations
      - Detection of non-deterministic operations
      - JSON serialization with round-trip verification
    acceptance_criteria:
      - runtime/replay_harness.py with all core classes
      - Trace capture during function execution
      - Serialization to/from JSON
      - Validation that replays match originals
      - Non-deterministic operation detection
      - Demo conformance test showing 3 iterations match
    stage: done
    commit_ref: 765741f

